                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Nashville</placeName>\n                                        <date>August 8/1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p><addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia, Pa.</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>Revd Sir,</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I transmit you by my friend<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Mr Lewis Hanf</persName> Ten <hi rend=\"sup\"\n                                                  >00</hi>/100 dolls., towards<lb/> my subscribed of\n                                        the Occident, &amp; should<lb/> this be not sufficient to\n                                        pay my dues<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Mr. Hanf</persName> will settle for the\n                                        Balance.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">You will very much oblige me, indeed,<lb/> if you\n                                        will please send me a german<lb/> &amp; polish prayer book\n                                        with the english trans<lb/>lation; also the 5 Books of\n                                        Moses,<lb/> translated in english. Should you not have<lb/>\n                                        these books on hand, send them to me, when<lb/> you receive\n                                        them, &amp; I will transmit the<lb/> money as soon as I get\n                                        them.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It is also very <sic>gratifieing</sic> to me,\n                                        to<lb/> be able to inform you that we have established<lb/>\n                                        here last year a Hebrew Benevolent Society,<lb/> (under the\n                                        name of <add>מגן דוד</add>) have bought ¾ acres<lb/> land\n                                        within 1 ½ miles from the city for a<lb/>\n                                        <add>ביד ניד</add> Our society is at present, very\n                                        small<lb/> yet, numbering only 5 families &amp; about 8\n                                        young men</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3qj78j1n/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
